title: The Zeppelin
description:
The Zeppelin is built around Gullwing Sidewinder trucks, with a narrow platform that delivers the rail-to-rail control needed for a supremely responsive ride and an exceptional carving experience.
L: 33.00"
W: 8.50"
WB: 23.50"
The Zeppelin comes with a Hawaiian Koa Topsheet, with artwork by Ryan Jacobs
